For your success, we not only carry new products such as complete rolls, rubberized rollers and rubber hoses as well as sleeves, rolls made of silicone and also roll cores made of a wide variety of materials. In many areas, the reconditioning of worn roller rubber linings in the form of re-rubberization and new rubber coatings is an option. This saves you a considerable amount of money - while maintaining the same level of quality.

Ask us about the best roller solution for you! Our specialists are always happy to help.

More than just rollers and roller rubber coverings
As a specialist for rubber compounds and rubber roller coverings, KRAIBURG offers you a number of special advantages in a unique combination:

The combination of the rubber know-how of an experienced manufacturer of rubber coatings or compounds and the precision of a performance- and quality-oriented roll production.
The expertise to develop roll covers and roll rubber linings to meet your specific needs, if required.
In addition, a surface program ranging from rough pre-ground to polished and super-finished, from crowning to grooving, depending on the desired finish.
Last but not least, as a customer you benefit from our complete range of rubber rollers (metal cores and rubber roller coverings) and can thus significantly reduce your workload!
As a customer, you benefit from the vast know-how of one of the leading rubber and roller specialists in the form of the KRAIBURG group of companies and its experts.

KRAIBURG Walzenfertigung GmbH offers customized rolls and rubber rollers. All rollers and elastomer or rubber coverings are manufactured by us specifically according to customer requirements based on years of experience. With our extensive know-how we develop new solutions for roller coverings and produce rollers and rubber rollers that inspire our customers.
