ng connection to its long tradition.The new logo retains iconic elements from the past, such as the globe and the font style, which symbolize the company''s solidity and international vision. At the same time, the more modern and clean lines reflect an increasingly dynamic corporate identity, focused on innovation.In parallel, the website has also been completely revamped to provide a more intuitive, modern, and functional browsing experience. With an improved structure, updated content, and enhanced accessibility, the new website allows visitors to easily explore the products, solutions, and services offered by Rosacometta. This evolution is necessary to effectively meet the needs of an increasingly digitized market.', hall = '13', stand = 'D63', logo_url = 'https://www.dynadot.com/tr/mainsite2023/navbar-logo-dark-2023.png', logo_file = 'logos/logo_EDILTECO_SpA.png', contact_persons = '[{"name": "Giulia Ortensi", "role": "Export Department", "email": "", "phone": "", "additional_info": ""}, {"name": "Olga Glushankova", "role": "Export Manager", "email": "", "phone": "", "additional_info": ""}, {"name": "Alice Guerzoni", "role": "Export Department", "email": "", "phone": "", "additional_info": ""}]'::jsonb, scraping_timestamp = '2025-09-18T00:40:11.132693', success = true, scraping_status = 'completed', data_source = 'ultimate_scraping'
