Altero Recycling Machinery S.L.
Smart Recycling. Real Results.

At ALTERO Recycling Machinery, we design and manufacture complete extrusion and pelletizing systems to transform plastic waste into high-quality recycled pellets. Headquartered near Barcelona, Spain, and with commercial presence in over 15 countries, we deliver flexible, energy-efficient, and optimized solutions for plastic recyclers and processors worldwide.

Founded by industry experts with over 20 years of experience in technical service, machine commissioning, and process optimization, ALTERO was created to offer a modern alternative to legacy recycling equipment manufacturers, with smarter engineering, quicker support, and seamless third-party integration capabilities.

Our systems are built for recyclers and converters dealing with:
Post-industrial and post-consumer waste (film, rigid, flakes, foams, etc.)
In-house scrap management and regranulation
Challenging materials

What makes ALTERO different:

High-Efficiency Extrusion Lines: Optimized for minimal degradation and maximum energy savings
Modular Pelletizing Systems: Feeding, screw design, filtration and pelletizing tailored to material type and output goals
Open Integration Architecture: Easily connects with upstream or downstream systems (wash lines, sorters, etc.)
Low CAPEX, Low OPEX: Competitive pricing without sacrificing European component quality
Global Support with a Personal Touch: Agile service and short lead times from our dedicated team

Innovation in Action:

We operate a fully equipped in-house test center, where clients from all over the world co-develop custom recycling solutions. We also collaborate with technology centers and industry leaders to push the boundaries of circularity, including new applications for recycled by-products and improved process stability.

Our Portfolio:

Complete pelletizing lines for PE, PP, PS, PA, PET, and more. VELOX for single stage, DUPLO for cascade configurations.
Single-screw extruders for recycling applications
Water Ring Pelletizers
Deodorization equipment, powered by FYCH.
PYROTECH lines for material preparation and stream optimization in chemical recycling.
Integration of underwater, air-cooled, and strand pelletizers
Tailor-made solutions for manufacturers, recyclers, compounders, and innovation teams.
Consulting and turnkey integration for new recycling operations

